    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Content Card Border Style",
      "target": "内容卡片边框样式"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "border treatment for the main editor card: glass (default — solid background with inset bevel + ring like callout cards), asymmetric (the original gradient with two corners highlighted), or full border (symmetric highlight)",
      "target": "主编辑器卡片的边框处理：玻璃（默认 — 实心背景带内凹斜面 + 类似标注卡片的环形）、不对称（原始渐变，两个角高亮）或完整边框（对称高亮）"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Floating View Header",
      "target": "浮动视图标题栏"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "the back/breadcrumb/action bar row floats over the note card instead of sitting above it, giving the note more vertical space",
      "target": "返回/面包屑/操作栏行浮动在笔记卡片上方，而非位于其上方，为笔记提供更多垂直空间"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
      "source": "Floating Header — Hover to Reveal",
      "target": "浮动标题栏 — 悬停显示"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "when floating header is enabled, hides the bar until you hover over the note card (requires floating view header to be on)",
      "target": "启用浮动标题栏后，将栏隐藏直到鼠标悬停在笔记卡片上（需要开启浮动视图标题栏）"
